Key Match Events: Darius Garland sank a 3-pointer with 45 seconds left and set up Jarrett Allen for a layup with 12.2 seconds remaining for the clincher
Miscellaneous Highlights: The Cavaliers equaled a franchise record set in 1976-77 with their eighth straight win to start the season
Others: Milwaukee, which played without star Giannis Antetokounmpo (adductor), lost its sixth game in a row since a season-opening win
